  "title": "Soothed Spiced Lebanese Chickpeas Hummus",
  "description": "This floral hummus soothes the sick day with aromatic spices and bright nuka-pickle. It blends chickpeas, vegetable stock, and a touch of lemon for a low calorie, comforting dip.",
