  "instructions": [
    "Rinse and drain the chickpeas, reserving the liquid for later.",
    "In a blender, combine chickpeas, tahini, garlic, lemon juice, and olive oil and pulse until smooth.",
    "Add vegetable stock gradually to achieve desired consistency.",
    "Stir in cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and pepper until well blended.",
    "Transfer to a serving bowl and swirl in the reserved pickled cucumber brine.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and a drizzle of olive oil.",
    "Let the hummus chill for at least 30 minutes to meld flavors.",
    "Serve with fresh veggies or low carb crackers."
